<subSubSection id="A0A4C0C489E4E4703DE43085AD418965" pageId="0" pageNumber="11" type="etymology">
<paragraph id="C818C748895484189E75FC86FDD1B291" pageId="0" pageNumber="11">Etymology.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="3715EB4D267D7DC27C956F74CF0ED195" pageId="0" pageNumber="11">The new species is named in honor of Prof. Arkady Lelej (Vladivostok, Russia), an outstanding hymenopterist and our friend.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="6FD928FF239712D1A82B54BF94773622" pageId="0" pageNumber="11" type="distribution">
<paragraph id="5E619CB60B636D846C45989F3FE5C34E" pageId="0" pageNumber="11">Distribution.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="1D4BD3C223F3CA847A2AF8E6A82D4D3E" pageId="0" pageNumber="11">Mongolia (Dornogovi, Sukhbaatar, Umnugovi).</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="530BAC36124179DC3D8F8D7199FE88CA" pageId="0" pageNumber="11" type="remarks">
<paragraph id="E1648EFD3A449D35B98DF8BE8D33CD1D" pageId="0" pageNumber="11">Remarks.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="26750C130E33BF39A733D19153EC415A" pageId="0" pageNumber="11">
It is noteworthy that two other cleptoparasitic genera, 
<taxonomicName id="F4C15BA9B788CC3C06410DB1C7F1B9BF" authorityName="Scopoli" authorityYear="1770" class="Insecta" family="Apidae" genus="Nomada" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Nomada" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="11" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="FBB664AE4F051E750FCE5EA19C3072BC" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="11">Nomada</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Scopoli, 1770 (
<taxonomicName id="96C745F543B2C7C6279E231FF6C72CE8" class="Insecta" family="Apidae" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="11" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="family">Apidae</taxonomicName>
) and 
<taxonomicName id="AE326D67AD40739819A90274A52CD0B1" authorityName="Latreille" authorityYear="1804" class="Insecta" family="Halictidae" genus="Sphecodes" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Sphecodes" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="11" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="FD20D59F1E6D7225B7DD891CCAD8EE11" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="11">Sphecodes</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(
<taxonomicName id="EAE6FB12D11463B34BD8640969918F1C" authorityName="Thomson" authorityYear="1869" class="Insecta" family="Halictidae" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="11" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="family">Halictidae</taxonomicName>
), also have a small group of species with two submarginal cells (
<bibRefCitation id="AA7CCEB8F720B077C3AD5E128D88F7B3" DOI="https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.2335.1.1" author="Proshchalykin, MYu" journalOrPublisher="Zootaxa" pageId="0" pageNumber="11" pagination="1 - 15" refId="B36" refString="Proshchalykin, MYu, Lelej, AS, 2010. Review of the Nomada roberjeotiana species-group (Hymenoptera: Apidae) of Russia, with description of new species. Zootaxa 2335: 1 - 15, DOI: https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.2335.1.1" title="Review of the Nomada roberjeotiana species-group (Hymenoptera: Apidae) of Russia, with description of new species." url="https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.2335.1.1" volume="2335" year="2010">Proshchalykin and Lelej 2010</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation id="1E4F2E1D6F89BFAB0C670DC4848C121B" DOI="https://doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.937.51708" author="Astafurova, YuV" journalOrPublisher="ZooKeys" pageId="0" pageNumber="11" pagination="31 - 88" refId="B5" refString="Astafurova, YuV, Proshchalykin, MYu, Schwarz, M, 2020. New and little-known species of the genus Sphecodes Latreille (Hymenoptera, Halictidae) from Southeast Asia. ZooKeys 937: 31 - 88, DOI: https://doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.937.51708" title="New and little-known species of the genus Sphecodes Latreille (Hymenoptera, Halictidae) from Southeast Asia." url="https://doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.937.51708" volume="937" year="2020">Astafurova et al. 2020</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
